---
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
import Heading from "../components/Heading.astro";
import Prose from "../components/Prose.astro";
---

<Layout title="About — Arijit's Blog" description="About Arijit's Blog.">
  <script slot="head" type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "AboutPage",
    "name": "About Arijit's Blog",
    "description": "About Arijit's Blog.",
    "url": new URL("/about", Astro.site).href,
    "isPartOf": {
      "@type": "WebSite",
      "name": "Arijit's Blog",
      "url": Astro.site?.href,
    },
  })} />
  <section class="about-container">
    <Heading as="h1">About Me</Heading>

    <Prose>

      <div class="experience-section">
        <!-- <Heading as="h2">Experience</Heading> -->
        <div class="experience-item">
          <p>Usually I create stuff with .NET and Angular. I would not say I am an expert, there are more experts in .NET and Angular out there. These are the technologies I work with daily from the start of my professional career. That's why these technologies became my default choice gradually. There are few other technologies I dabble with occasionally, sometimes it's Python, C or C++, when it suits the topic I am engage with.</p>
          <p>Being empty-handed is very frustrating for me, it's better to do something than nothing. That's why after finishing my study, I took a job at corporate. But the thing is, I am very lazy as well, I prefer to sit on my chair or lie down on my couch, and try to reduce the burden put on my head by corporates. And obviously for that corporate pays me well.</p>
          <p>
            At Hyland Software, I am involved in developing and maintaining enterprise software solutions using C# .NET and Angular. 
            Collaborating with cross-functional teams to deliver high-quality applications that serve 
            thousands of users worldwide.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skills-section">
        <Heading as="h2">Technical Skills</Heading>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Primary:</strong> C# .NET, Angular</li>
          <li><strong>Languages:</strong> Python, Java, Kotlin, C, C++</li>
          <li><strong>Web:</strong> HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, TypeScript</li>
          <li><strong>Tools:</strong> Git, SQL Server, Docker, Azure</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-section">
        <Heading as="h2">Get In Touch</Heading>
        <p>I'm always open to discussing new opportunities, interesting projects, or just having a chat about technology.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>LinkedIn: <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/arikundu9" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">linkedin.com/in/arikundu9<span class="sr-only"> (opens in a new tab)</span></a></li>
          <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/arklnd" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github.com/arklnd<span class="sr-only"> (opens in a new tab)</span></a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </Prose>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .experience-item h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .skills-section ul, .contact-section ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .skills-section li, .contact-section li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>
